[{"Code":"en","Title":"Invite team members","Slug":"invite-team-members","ContentType":2,"Content":"<p data-block-id=\"a6f2e62f-498f-4a81-964c-8989142145ee\">With xenPlatform activated, you can invite your team members to access your sub-accounts’ dashboards. A common use case is to grant users on the Platform accounts access to sub-accounts as well. Only members with the Admin permission have access to this feature.</p><p data-block-id=\"69ce4d64-588c-4e2c-8510-e93a0b9b1894\"><img data-block-id=\"8bad8f36-c616-4620-9cea-25af9da407cd\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/pum-team-members-demo_hehetr.webp\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"716\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:716px;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"2dd2d4ab-e2f2-411a-83eb-2d41e1ab5c0b\">All of your team members that have access to your platform account or any of the accounts you have created will be visible in this Team Members page.</p><h2 data-block-id=\"ec2c3165-9e18-464e-a645-e7b2ef8375db\">Inviting a new team member</h2><ol data-block-id=\"mcrtbor3-dxyw08-001\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"mcrtbor3-hdh1ot-002\"><p data-block-id=\"mcrtbvpy-wrxbck-003\">Click <strong>Add Member</strong> on the top-right corner of the Team Members page.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"769ca96f-9c44-4c7e-9655-68150033dfad\"><p data-block-id=\"073244cd-8fa2-477b-a669-19f614a3d65e\">Enter the <strong>email address </strong>of the team member you want to invite, then click <code>Next</code></p></li><li data-block-id=\"3707a542-1836-4825-875d-54a320f13250\"><p data-block-id=\"98cf164e-0803-4d89-acc3-a547e8ad7aac\">Select the <strong>account </strong>you want this team member to get access to</p></li><li data-block-id=\"2d730a40-fb15-446d-b45e-9faa1eed1486\"><p data-block-id=\"96404c02-83fd-4272-9c59-ff6e0a34cd4b\">Select the <strong>permissions </strong>that this team member will have for the chosen account</p></li></ol><p data-block-id=\"f25249e3-c88f-48e0-b5fb-a4e4fa6fc1d7\"><img data-block-id=\"91afd4e9-6ed7-41d8-872b-778b4d897a24\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/pum-tutorial-1_h4szu1.gif\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"672\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:672px;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"bbe795b4-5d9b-4d8e-b0c5-84b1454688e3\">Alternatively, you can invite a team member to your accounts from the xenPlatform accounts page:</p><ol data-block-id=\"0ad27e26-246e-48a6-9641-371324d03b4b\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"b0f57c95-1cd9-46ba-95c1-6ef7ce4b37e0\"><p data-block-id=\"fde23147-93c5-4626-b9f5-96bffdd945d9\">Find the account you want the team member to access</p></li><li data-block-id=\"8173136d-ec82-4aad-a00f-66c89baf64e1\"><p data-block-id=\"a15c67d8-720c-4a98-9ba9-4cafa20dca8e\">Click on the options button on the right, and select <code>Add member</code></p></li></ol><h2 data-block-id=\"e28551ac-cc7d-47e9-8714-5eabd9f12dba\">Editing user access and permissions</h2><p data-block-id=\"ce532d59-91ab-4c8a-b494-76191fe31b2b\">From the Team Members page, you can click on the Edit button for any existing team member. From this team member details page, you can:</p><ul data-block-id=\"5b06e087-ca0c-4299-bbb6-40fc60e41098\" style=\"\"><li data-block-id=\"fdf4951d-ad36-455c-8777-84df50fa0c31\"><p data-block-id=\"10f3532f-d99a-4c30-9f7a-2b016162f897\">Invite your team members to more accounts</p></li><li data-block-id=\"52d8ce5e-0901-48d1-85c6-fd0521868236\"><p data-block-id=\"28f4aa8f-fc62-401e-adf4-e5f8556d81cd\">Edit your team member’s permissions on each account</p></li><li data-block-id=\"3121e81b-35f7-404e-b80c-057abc2902eb\"><p data-block-id=\"a4c102cb-abb2-4f0c-85f6-35caea12b117\">Remove their access to each account</p></li></ul><h2 data-block-id=\"74aafa5d-a973-42ef-a79f-39913345bd12\">Permissions available for sub-account users</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"664\" class=\"table-auto overflow-x-auto border border-slate-300 editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:664px;width:664px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:199px;\"><col style=\"width:199px;\"><col style=\"width:266px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"199\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 text-center align-middle\"><p data-block-id=\"8ab46640-1fc5-453c-8f09-0df75a7328e1\"><strong>Permissio</strong>n</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"199\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 text-center align-middle\"><p data-block-id=\"0989835c-0da5-4c27-b5d0-4d8d0b68b5a3\">Managed</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"266\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 text-center align-middle\"><p data-block-id=\"2b7cd112-937b-418d-b224-2ce4d53f3cb2\">Owned</p></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"199\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"c9d15371-b394-4559-986e-77cd9adef469\">View</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"199\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"5b8a831c-ff91-46ca-9b28-58d09437e400\">✅</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"266\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"a937c275-580d-46a2-99b9-c648e1185f13\">✅</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"199\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"4b9f2137-77ce-4d1f-9490-df54adcd432d\">Edit</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"199\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"736ddcc4-13d8-4bfa-8add-4f0cdfcdd2bd\">✅</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"266\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"93b46133-1089-4fc5-901c-93d015bd9b85\">✅</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"199\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"1fc16b2b-05ba-485a-bafd-d7a1e6ee8c6b\">Approve</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"199\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"64f38cc5-f483-4f52-acf6-6641aeb6dede\">✅</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"266\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"230dd813-3302-413e-96f0-aaedba97a1bd\">✅</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"199\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"34272470-edee-45b6-8fab-f052c1dc8b47\">Admin</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"199\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"7c2fb769-1884-4891-8381-e26f4f472188\">✅</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"266\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"18fe622e-600a-40ef-ab07-bf6e979d5e61\">✅</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"199\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"6eea589a-a379-4e55-9963-f7ef6841f407\">Developer</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"199\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"2e1d1ce9-3ecf-4497-9a9b-17894c0b1ba2\">✅</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"266\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"e732ef6a-5cec-4a2a-85df-d9b74481f3c5\">❌</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"199\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"5da918bc-513f-4ed8-b457-9ff052417616\">Withdraw</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"199\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"67982b80-02c9-460a-9b9a-81d44664307a\">✅</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"266\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"fbb9e690-6aa1-4bb1-899c-4b135160eaec\">✅</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"199\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"97817049-5edc-4f06-9342-05fa387b111b\">No balance</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"199\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"8fa286e2-972b-462c-a8b9-630acaad25f0\">✅</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"266\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"06dd18f4-f51f-421a-81f9-780f7262f03f\">✅</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p data-block-id=\"4dea53ff-eb58-4af1-afc4-b42313bde7ef\">The Developer permission is not available for Owned accounts, hence these accounts will not be able to generate their own API keys or set their own callbacks. The Platform can use their API keys instead to set callbacks for Owned accounts via API.</p><p data-block-id=\"9ffd41a2-db70-468b-be09-057af54b861b\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Invite team members","Description":null},{"Code":"id","Title":"Undang anggota tim","Slug":"invite-team-members","ContentType":2,"Content":"<p data-block-id=\"mcrnt3w1-tcx785-002\">Setelah xenPlatform aktif, Anda dapat mengundang anggota tim Anda untuk mengakses dasbor sub-akun Anda. Kasus penggunaan umum adalah untuk memberi pengguna di akun Platform akses ke sub-akun juga. Hanya anggota dengan izin Admin yang memiliki akses ke fitur ini.</p><p data-block-id=\"mcrnt3w1-yd38vs-003\"><img data-block-id=\"mcrnt3w2-6pvtrz-004\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/pum-team-members-demo_hehetr.webp\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"716\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:716px;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mcrnt3w2-b0a7ry-005\">Semua anggota tim Anda yang memiliki akses ke akun platform Anda atau salah satu akun yang telah Anda buat akan terlihat di halaman Anggota Tim ini.</p><h2 data-block-id=\"mcrta1gu-a76x4z-001\">Cara undang anggota tim baru</h2><ol data-block-id=\"mcrta9xr-ut6wyf-002\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"mcrta9xr-q0vq41-003\"><p data-block-id=\"mcrnt3w2-520km7-007\">Klik <strong>Tambah Anggota</strong> di kanan atas halaman Anggota Tim.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mcrnt3w2-h9ibj3-009\"><p data-block-id=\"mcrnt3w2-pw07ii-010\">Masukkan <strong>email</strong> anggota tim yang ingin Anda undang, lalu klik <code>Next</code></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mcrnt3w2-ge5ll8-011\"><p data-block-id=\"mcrnt3w3-dba1w1-012\">Pilih <strong>akun yang Anda inginkan</strong> untuk diakses oleh anggota tim ini</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mcrnt3w3-i3akjp-013\"><p data-block-id=\"mcrnt3w3-zan9yv-014\">Pilih <strong>izin</strong> yang akan dimiliki anggota tim ini untuk akun yang dipilih</p></li></ol><p data-block-id=\"mcrnt3w3-w513dz-015\"><img data-block-id=\"mcrnt3w3-3tz3aa-016\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/pum-tutorial-1_h4szu1.gif\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"672\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:672px;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mcrnt3w3-swqj21-017\">Atau, Anda dapat mengundang anggota tim ke akun Anda dari halaman akun xenPlatform:</p><ol data-block-id=\"mcrnt3w3-a4e3v4-018\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"mcrnt3w3-t5yr7u-019\"><p data-block-id=\"mcrnt3w3-gi7vzh-020\">Temukan akun yang Anda inginkan untuk diakses oleh anggota tim</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mcrnt3w3-c89mqi-021\"><p data-block-id=\"mcrnt3w3-e7icqr-022\">Klik tombol opsi di sebelah kanan, dan pilih <code>Add member</code></p></li></ol><h2 data-block-id=\"mcrnt3w3-z5o887-023\">Mengedit akses dan izin pengguna</h2><p data-block-id=\"mcrnt3w3-je2it1-024\">Dari halaman Anggota Tim, Anda dapat mengklik tombol Edit untuk anggota tim yang ada. Dari halaman detail anggota tim ini, Anda dapat:</p><ul data-block-id=\"mcrnt3w3-0iw8ia-025\" style=\"\"><li data-block-id=\"mcrnt3w3-9o01n7-026\"><p data-block-id=\"mcrnt3w3-q7r13s-027\">Mengundang anggota tim Anda ke lebih banyak akun</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mcrnt3w3-hso1ze-028\"><p data-block-id=\"mcrnt3w3-8xngyp-029\">Mengedit izin anggota tim Anda di setiap akun</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mcrnt3w3-l4mwet-030\"><p data-block-id=\"mcrnt3w3-78ikbo-031\">Menghapus akses mereka ke setiap akun</p></li></ul><h2 data-block-id=\"mcrnt3w3-f39zoo-032\">Izin tersedia untuk pengguna sub-akun</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"664\" class=\"table-auto overflow-x-auto border border-slate-300 editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:664px;width:664px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:199px;\"><col style=\"width:199px;\"><col style=\"width:266px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"199\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 text-center align-middle\"><p data-block-id=\"mcrtgt1r-4hbg3d-090\"><strong>Izin</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"199\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 text-center align-middle\"><p data-block-id=\"mcrtgt1r-fu8s14-091\">Managed</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"266\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 text-center align-middle\"><p data-block-id=\"mcrtgt1r-yef6k3-092\">Owned</p></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"199\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"mcrtgt1s-jerz8e-093\">View</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"199\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"mcrtgt1s-lf5h71-094\">✅</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"266\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"mcrtgt1s-b50knd-095\">✅</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"199\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"mcrtgt1s-0rfh24-096\">Edit</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"199\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"mcrtgt1s-wv0crm-097\">✅</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"266\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"mcrtgt1s-wcx3ej-098\">✅</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"199\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"mcrtgt1s-zjwqgx-099\">Approve</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"199\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"mcrtgt1s-lilvro-100\">✅</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"266\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"mcrtgt1t-dhun87-101\">✅</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"199\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"mcrtgt1t-pgqsx7-102\">Admin</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"199\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"mcrtgt1t-u5j3zy-103\">✅</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"266\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"mcrtgt1t-xlhygw-104\">✅</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"199\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"mcrtgt1t-0u57ie-105\">Developer</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"199\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"mcrtgt1t-9qaxs9-106\">✅</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"266\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"mcrtgt1t-1ubyf4-107\">❌</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"199\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"mcrtgt1t-wjo0e9-108\">Withdraw</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"199\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"mcrtgt1u-sd2zrv-109\">✅</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"266\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"mcrtgt1u-s4l8b7-110\">✅</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"199\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"mcrtgt1u-s1z5nz-111\">No balance</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"199\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"mcrtgt1u-gehl8a-112\">✅</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"266\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"mcrtgt1u-jq86t4-113\">✅</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p data-block-id=\"mcrnt3w9-0xxmep-057\"><strong>Catatan:</strong> Izin Developer tidak tersedia untuk akun yang Owned, oleh karena itu akun ini tidak akan dapat membuat API key atau mengatur callback mereka sendiri. Platform dapat menggunakan API key mereka untuk mengatur callback untuk akun Owned melalui API.</p><p data-block-id=\"mcrnt3w9-ms3e3z-058\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Undang anggota tim","Description":null},{"Code":"th","Title":"เชิญสมาชิกในทีม","Slug":"inviting-team-members","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><p data-block-id=\"a6f2e62f-498f-4a81-964c-8989142145ee\">เมื่อเปิดใช้งาน xenPlatform คุณสามารถเชิญสมาชิกในทีมของคุณให้เข้าถึงแดชบอร์ดของบัญชีย่อย (sub-accounts) ของคุณได้ กรณีการใช้งานทั่วไปคือการให้สิทธิ์ผู้ใช้ในบัญชี Platform เข้าถึงบัญชีย่อยได้เช่นกัน เฉพาะสมาชิกที่มีสิทธิ์ Admin เท่านั้นที่สามารถเข้าถึงคุณสมบัตินี้ได้</p><p data-block-id=\"69ce4d64-588c-4e2c-8510-e93a0b9b1894\"><img data-block-id=\"8bad8f36-c616-4620-9cea-25af9da407cd\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/pum-team-members-demo_hehetr.webp\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt width=\"716\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link newtab style=\"width:716px;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"2dd2d4ab-e2f2-411a-83eb-2d41e1ab5c0b\">สมาชิกในทีมทั้งหมดของคุณที่สามารถเข้าถึงบัญชี Platform ของคุณ หรือบัญชีใด ๆ ที่คุณสร้างขึ้น จะแสดงอยู่ในหน้าสมาชิกในทีม (Team Members) นี้</p><h2 data-block-id=\"ec2c3165-9e18-464e-a645-e7b2ef8375db\">การเชิญสมาชิกในทีมใหม่</h2><ol data-block-id=\"mcrtbor3-dxyw08-001\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"mcrtbor3-hdh1ot-002\"><p data-block-id=\"mcrtbvpy-wrxbck-003\">คลิก <strong>Add Member</strong> ที่มุมบนขวาของหน้าสมาชิกในทีม (Team Members)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"769ca96f-9c44-4c7e-9655-68150033dfad\"><p data-block-id=\"073244cd-8fa2-477b-a669-19f614a3d65e\">ป้อน <strong>ที่อยู่อีเมล (email address) </strong>ของสมาชิกในทีมที่คุณต้องการเชิญ จากนั้นคลิก <code>Next</code></p></li><li data-block-id=\"3707a542-1836-4825-875d-54a320f13250\"><p data-block-id=\"98cf164e-0803-4d89-acc3-a547e8ad7aac\">เลือก <strong>บัญชี (account) </strong>ที่คุณต้องการให้สมาชิกในทีมนี้เข้าถึง</p></li><li data-block-id=\"2d730a40-fb15-446d-b45e-9faa1eed1486\"><p data-block-id=\"96404c02-83fd-4272-9c59-ff6e0a34cd4b\">เลือก <strong>สิทธิ์ (permissions) </strong>ที่สมาชิกในทีมนี้จะมีสำหรับบัญชีที่เลือก</p></li></ol><p data-block-id=\"f25249e3-c88f-48e0-b5fb-a4e4fa6fc1d7\"><img data-block-id=\"91afd4e9-6ed7-41d8-872b-778b4d897a24\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/pum-tutorial-1_h4szu1.gif\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt width=\"672\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link newtab style=\"width:672px;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"bbe795b4-5d9b-4d8e-b0c5-84b1454688e3\">อีกทางเลือกหนึ่ง คุณสามารถเชิญสมาชิกในทีมเข้าสู่บัญชีของคุณได้จากหน้าบัญชี xenPlatform:</p><ol data-block-id=\"0ad27e26-246e-48a6-9641-371324d03b4b\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"b0f57c95-1cd9-46ba-95c1-6ef7ce4b37e0\"><p data-block-id=\"fde23147-93c5-4626-b9f5-96bffdd945d9\">ค้นหาบัญชีที่คุณต้องการให้สมาชิกในทีมเข้าถึง</p></li><li data-block-id=\"8173136d-ec82-4aad-a00f-66c89baf64e1\"><p data-block-id=\"a15c67d8-720c-4a98-9ba9-4cafa20dca8e\">คลิกที่ปุ่มตัวเลือกทางด้านขวา และเลือก <code>Add member</code></p></li></ol><h2 data-block-id=\"e28551ac-cc7d-47e9-8714-5eabd9f12dba\">การแก้ไขสิทธิ์การเข้าถึงและสิทธิ์ของผู้ใช้</h2><p data-block-id=\"ce532d59-91ab-4c8a-b494-76191fe31b2b\">จากหน้าสมาชิกในทีม (Team Members) คุณสามารถคลิกที่ปุ่ม Edit สำหรับสมาชิกในทีมที่มีอยู่ จากหน้ารายละเอียดสมาชิกในทีมนี้ คุณสามารถ:</p><ul data-block-id=\"5b06e087-ca0c-4299-bbb6-40fc60e41098\" style><li data-block-id=\"fdf4951d-ad36-455c-8777-84df50fa0c31\"><p data-block-id=\"10f3532f-d99a-4c30-9f7a-2b016162f897\">เชิญสมาชิกในทีมของคุณไปยังบัญชีอื่น ๆ เพิ่มเติม</p></li><li data-block-id=\"52d8ce5e-0901-48d1-85c6-fd0521868236\"><p data-block-id=\"28f4aa8f-fc62-401e-adf4-e5f8556d81cd\">แก้ไขสิทธิ์ (permissions) ของสมาชิกในทีมของคุณในแต่ละบัญชี</p></li><li data-block-id=\"3121e81b-35f7-404e-b80c-057abc2902eb\"><p data-block-id=\"a4c102cb-abb2-4f0c-85f6-35caea12b117\">ลบสิทธิ์การเข้าถึงของพวกเขาในแต่ละบัญชี</p></li></ul><h2 data-block-id=\"74aafa5d-a973-42ef-a79f-39913345bd12\">สิทธิ์ (Permissions) ที่มีให้สำหรับผู้ใช้บัญชีย่อย (sub-account)</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"664\" class=\"table-auto overflow-x-auto border border-slate-300 editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:664px;width:664px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:199px;\"><col style=\"width:199px;\"><col style=\"width:266px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"199\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 text-center align-middle\"><p data-block-id=\"8ab46640-1fc5-453c-8f09-0df75a7328e1\"><strong>Permissio</strong>n</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"199\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 text-center align-middle\"><p data-block-id=\"0989835c-0da5-4c27-b5d0-4d8d0b68b5a3\">Managed</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"266\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 text-center align-middle\"><p data-block-id=\"2b7cd112-937b-418d-b224-2ce4d53f3cb2\">Owned</p></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"199\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"c9d15371-b394-4559-986e-77cd9adef469\">View</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"199\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"5b8a831c-ff91-46ca-9b28-58d09437e400\">&#x2705;</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"266\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"a937c275-580d-46a2-99b9-c648e1185f13\">&#x2705;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"199\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"4b9f2137-77ce-4d1f-9490-df54adcd432d\">Edit</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"199\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"736ddcc4-13d8-4bfa-8add-4f0cdfcdd2bd\">&#x2705;</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"266\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"93b46133-1089-4fc5-901c-93d015bd9b85\">&#x2705;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"199\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"1fc16b2b-05ba-485a-bafd-d7a1e6ee8c6b\">Approve</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"199\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"64f38cc5-f483-4f52-acf6-6641aeb6dede\">&#x2705;</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"266\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"230dd813-3302-413e-96f0-aaedba97a1bd\">&#x2705;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"199\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"34272470-edee-45b6-8fab-f052c1dc8b47\">Admin</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"199\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"7c2fb769-1884-4891-8381-e26f4f472188\">&#x2705;</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"266\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"18fe622e-600a-40ef-ab07-bf6e979d5e61\">&#x2705;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"199\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"6eea589a-a379-4e55-9963-f7ef6841f407\">Developer</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"199\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"2e1d1ce9-3ecf-4497-9a9b-17894c0b1ba2\">&#x2705;</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"266\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"e732ef6a-5cec-4a2a-85df-d9b74481f3c5\">&#x274c;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"199\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"5da918bc-513f-4ed8-b457-9ff052417616\">Withdraw</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"199\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"67982b80-02c9-460a-9b9a-81d44664307a\">&#x2705;</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"266\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"fbb9e690-6aa1-4bb1-899c-4b135160eaec\">&#x2705;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"199\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"97817049-5edc-4f06-9342-05fa387b111b\">No balance</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"199\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"8fa286e2-972b-462c-a8b9-630acaad25f0\">&#x2705;</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"266\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"06dd18f4-f51f-421a-81f9-780f7262f03f\">&#x2705;</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p data-block-id=\"4dea53ff-eb58-4af1-afc4-b42313bde7ef\">สิทธิ์ Developer ไม่สามารถใช้ได้สำหรับบัญชี Owned ดังนั้นบัญชีเหล่านี้จะไม่สามารถสร้าง API keys ของตนเอง หรือตั้งค่า callbacks ของตนเองได้ Platform สามารถใช้ API keys ของตนเองเพื่อตั้งค่า callbacks สำหรับบัญชี Owned ผ่าน API ได้แทน</p><p data-block-id=\"9ffd41a2-db70-468b-be09-057af54b861b\"></p>","SeoTitle":"เชิญสมาชิกในทีม","Description":null},{"Code":"es-mx","Title":"Invitar a miembros del equipo","Slug":"invite-team-members","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><p data-block-id=\"a6f2e62f-498f-4a81-964c-8989142145ee\">Con xenPlatform activado, usted puede invitar a los miembros de su equipo a acceder a los paneles de control de sus subcuentas. Un caso de uso común es otorgar acceso a las subcuentas a los usuarios de las cuentas de la Platform. Solo los miembros con el permiso de Admin tienen acceso a esta función.</p><p data-block-id=\"69ce4d64-588c-4e2c-8510-e93a0b9b1894\"><img data-block-id=\"8bad8f36-c616-4620-9cea-25af9da407cd\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/pum-team-members-demo_hehetr.webp\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"716\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link newtab style=\"width:716px;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"2dd2d4ab-e2f2-411a-83eb-2d41e1ab5c0b\">Todos los miembros de su equipo que tienen acceso a su cuenta de plataforma o a cualquiera de las cuentas que usted ha creado serán visibles en esta página de Miembros del Equipo.</p><h2 data-block-id=\"ec2c3165-9e18-464e-a645-e7b2ef8375db\">Invitar a un nuevo miembro del equipo</h2><ol data-block-id=\"mcrtbor3-dxyw08-001\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"mcrtbor3-hdh1ot-002\"><p data-block-id=\"mcrtbvpy-wrxbck-003\">Haga clic en <strong>Agregar Miembro</strong> en la esquina superior derecha de la página Miembros del Equipo.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"769ca96f-9c44-4c7e-9655-68150033dfad\"><p data-block-id=\"073244cd-8fa2-477b-a669-19f614a3d65e\">Ingrese el <strong>correo electrónico</strong> del miembro del equipo que desea invitar, luego haga clic en <code>Next</code></p></li><li data-block-id=\"3707a542-1836-4825-875d-54a320f13250\"><p data-block-id=\"98cf164e-0803-4d89-acc3-a547e8ad7aac\">Seleccione la <strong>cuenta</strong> a la que desea que acceda este miembro del equipo</p></li><li data-block-id=\"2d730a40-fb15-446d-b45e-9faa1eed1486\"><p data-block-id=\"96404c02-83fd-4272-9c59-ff6e0a34cd4b\">Seleccione los <strong>permisos</strong> que tendrá este miembro del equipo para la cuenta elegida</p></li></ol><p data-block-id=\"f25249e3-c88f-48e0-b5fb-a4e4fa6fc1d7\"><img data-block-id=\"91afd4e9-6ed7-41d8-872b-778b4d897a24\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/pum-tutorial-1_h4szu1.gif\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"672\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link newtab style=\"width:672px;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"bbe795b4-5d9b-4d8e-b0c5-84b1454688e3\">Alternativamente, usted puede invitar a un miembro del equipo a sus cuentas desde la página de cuentas de xenPlatform:</p><ol data-block-id=\"0ad27e26-246e-48a6-9641-371324d03b4b\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"b0f57c95-1cd9-46ba-95c1-6ef7ce4b37e0\"><p data-block-id=\"fde23147-93c5-4626-b9f5-96bffdd945d9\">Encuentre la cuenta a la que desea que acceda el miembro del equipo</p></li><li data-block-id=\"8173136d-ec82-4aad-a00f-66c89baf64e1\"><p data-block-id=\"a15c67d8-720c-4a98-9ba9-4cafa20dca8e\">Haga clic en el botón de opciones a la derecha y seleccione <code>Add member</code></p></li></ol><h2 data-block-id=\"e28551ac-cc7d-47e9-8714-5eabd9f12dba\">Edición de acceso y permisos de usuario</h2><p data-block-id=\"ce532d59-91ab-4c8a-b494-76191fe1b2b\">Desde la página Miembros del Equipo, usted puede hacer clic en el botón Editar para cualquier miembro del equipo existente. Desde esta página de detalles del miembro del equipo, usted puede:</p><ul data-block-id=\"5b06e087-ca0c-4299-bbb6-40fc60e41098\" style><li data-block-id=\"fdf4951d-ad36-455c-8777-84df50fa0c31\"><p data-block-id=\"10f3532f-d99a-4c30-9f7a-2b016162f897\">Invitar a sus miembros del equipo a más cuentas</p></li><li data-block-id=\"52d8ce5e-0901-48d1-85c6-fd0521868236\"><p data-block-id=\"28f4aa8f-fc62-401e-adf4-e5f8556d81cd\">Editar los permisos de su miembro del equipo en cada cuenta</p></li><li data-block-id=\"3121e81b-35f7-404e-b80c-057abc2902eb\"><p data-block-id=\"a4c102cb-abb2-4f0c-85f6-35caea12b117\">Eliminar su acceso a cada cuenta</p></li></ul><h2 data-block-id=\"74aafa5d-a973-42ef-a79f-39913345bd12\">Permisos disponibles para usuarios de subcuentas</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"664\" class=\"table-auto overflow-x-auto border border-slate-300 editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:664px;width:664px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:199px;\"><col style=\"width:199px;\"><col style=\"width:266px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"199\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 text-center align-middle\"><p data-block-id=\"8ab46640-1fc5-453c-8f09-0df75a7328e1\"><strong>Permiso</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"199\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 text-center align-middle\"><p data-block-id=\"0989835c-0da5-4c27-b5d0-4d8d0b68b5a3\">Administrada</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"266\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 text-center align-middle\"><p data-block-id=\"2b7cd112-937b-418d-b224-2ce4d53f3cb2\">Propia</p></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"199\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"c9d15371-b394-4559-986e-77cd9adef469\">Ver</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"199\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"5b8a831c-ff91-46ca-9b28-58d09437e400\">&#x2705;</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"266\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"a937c275-580d-46a2-99b9-c648e1185f13\">&#x2705;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"199\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"4b9f2137-77ce-4d1f-9490-df54adcd432d\">Editar</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"199\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"736ddcc4-13d8-4bfa-8add-4f0cdfcdd2bd\">&#x2705;</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"266\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"93b46133-1089-4fc5-901c-93d015bd9b85\">&#x2705;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"199\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"1fc16b2b-05ba-485a-bafd-d7a1e6ee8c6b\">Aprobar</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"199\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"64f38cc5-f483-4f52-acf6-6641aeb6dede\">&#x2705;</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"266\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"230dd813-3302-413e-96f0-aaedba97a1bd\">&#x2705;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"199\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"34272470-edee-45b6-8fab-f052c1dc8b47\">Admin</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"199\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"7c2fb769-1884-4891-8381-e26f4f472188\">&#x2705;</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"266\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"18fe622e-600a-40ef-ab07-bf6e979d5e61\">&#x2705;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"199\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"6eea589a-a379-4e55-9963-f7ef6841f407\">Developer</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"199\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"2e1d1ce9-3ecf-4497-9a9b-17894c0b1ba2\">&#x2705;</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"266\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"e732ef6a-5cec-4a2a-85df-d9b74481f3c5\">&#x274c;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"199\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"5da918bc-513f-4ed8-b457-9ff052417616\">Retirar</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"199\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"67982b80-02c9-460a-9b9a-81d44664307a\">&#x2705;</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"266\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"fbb9e690-6aa1-4bb1-899c-4b135160eaec\">&#x2705;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"199\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"97817049-5edc-4f06-9342-05fa387b111b\">Sin saldo</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"199\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"8fa286e2-972b-462c-a8b9-630acaad25f0\">&#x2705;</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"266\" class=\"border border-slate-300 p-2 whitespace-pre-line\"><p data-block-id=\"06dd18f4-f51f-421a-81f9-780f7262f03f\">&#x2705;</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p data-block-id=\"4dea53ff-eb58-4af1-afc4-b42313bde7ef\">El permiso Developer no está disponible para cuentas Propias, por lo tanto, estas cuentas no podrán generar sus propias API keys ni establecer sus propios callbacks. La Platform puede usar sus API keys en su lugar para establecer callbacks para cuentas Propias a través de la API.</p><p data-block-id=\"9ffd41a2-db70-466b-be09-057af54b861b\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Invitar a miembros del equipo","Description":null}]